# Custom Voices Directory

Place your custom voice reference audio files here for voice cloning.

## Supported Formats
- WAV (16kHz, mono recommended)
- MP3 (will be converted)
- FLAC

## File Naming
- Use descriptive names: `my_singer_voice.wav`
- The name (without extension) will be used as the voice identifier

## Requirements
- Clean audio with minimal background noise
- 30-60 seconds of voice/singing
- Consistent pitch and tone
- Avoid reverb or echo

## Usage
1. Place your audio file in this directory.
2. The system will automatically detect it when you train a voice.
3. You can also upload through the web interface.

## Example
- `john_doe_voice.wav`
- `rock_singer.wav`
